to escape reality

06:33.627 --> 06:34.762
'cause reality hurts

06:34.795 --> 06:36.296
when the whole family
isn't together.

06:38.432 --> 06:42.803
Shania, I just want you to be
you, 'cause you're awesome.

06:44.004 --> 06:46.740
